Start Redis Server (WSL)
 search in window + s: wsl
 run this command :redis-server

now in vs code run this in terminal 1:
celery -A medical_shop worker -l info -P solo 
Note: -P solo is required when running Celery on Windows.


start django server in other terminal 


Terminal Setup Summary

During development you should have three terminals running:

Terminal 1 – Redis

    wsl
    redis-server
    redis-cli ping

Terminal 2 – Celery Worker

    celery -A medical_shop worker -l info -P solo

Terminal 3 – Django Server

    python manage.py runserver